    <item>
      <title>黑石集团收购中城办公楼 重返纽约办公楼市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-30/blackstone-set-for-new-york-office-comeback-with-midtown-tower</link>
      <description><![CDATA[黑石公司即将达成协议，收购曼哈顿中城的一座大厦，这将标志着这家全球最大房地产投资者重返纽约写字楼交易市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-30/blackstone-set-for-new-york-office-comeback-with-midtown-tower</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 Jan 2025 10:51:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>黑石集团向加拿大富人寻求帮助，扩大 BXPE 的影响力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/blackstone-turns-to-canada-s-wealthy-to-broaden-bxpe-s-reach</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，黑石公司通过一项针对加拿大富裕投资者的融资活动筹集了 6.3 亿美元，使其首只个人私募股权基金的资产规模达到约 85 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/blackstone-turns-to-canada-s-wealthy-to-broaden-bxpe-s-reach</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 Jan 2025 21:40:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
